To run tests you first need to install Python 3.8 (if it's not) and python package manager pip.


To install required libraries in command line run to a directory with downloaded project and run next command:

pip3 install -r requirements.txt


To run all tests just type next command without any parameters in command line in api_tests directory:

pytest


To run desired test with command line run:

pytest <name_of_desired_test>